{"tid":1273293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會即刻讀宣言同訴求呀！唔讀你衝入去係無意義架！","createTime":"2019-07-01T13:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T14:25:42.000Z","uid":6435,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a71dc59074e3b86afabc2f58364b8e4121b90b24","tid":1273293,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"求下大家傳比前線知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0bd8caa296456d836dcc42c60366ecbade5fbd","tid":1273293,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f13b9714a9aeea7df61c9d3e6a58ac0956ea5232","tid":1273293,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593a76f417d5293117c601e18331e93c25c88073","tid":1273293,"uid":63240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"金鐘宣言 / 香港人民爭取其應有之普世價值及社會制度宣言<br />\n<br />\n希望有立法會議員或政黨領袖<br />\n能夠係聽日／未來遊行示威中，或者係立法會中，向全世界朗讀出以下代表香港人民聲音之宣言<br />\n<br />\n1. 對於過去數日，以至近數年之港人抗爭運動，皆為香港人為爭取自己應有的權利，所作出之公民抗命活動，所有熱愛香港的人民將一直支持此等抗爭直到永遠<br />\n<br />\n2. 謹代表香港人民宣誓，香港人民將永遠以追求本來應有之普世價值及社會制度為己任<br />\n<br />\n3. 對於行政，立法，司法機關等，香港人民已無法容忍，若不立即進行改革，人民必將舉起手中的武器及盾牌，推翻暴政，推翻議會<br />\n<br />\n4. 沒有民主選舉是一切問題之根源，必須馬上修改立法會議席及行政長官產生辦法，若非落實全民普選，誓不罷休<br />\n<br />\n5. 各大政府組織內部腐敗不堪，要求相關領導人士立即道歉，下台<br />\n<br />\n6. 要求政府立即釋放相關被捕示威者及政治犯，還他們一個清白<br />\n<br />\n7. 政府必須承諾追究警隊以不當武力鎮壓示威者，警隊必須向全港市民致歉<br />\n<br />\n8. 於立法會提出議案，必須將近年運動定性為公民抗命民主運動，而非暴動<br />\n<br />\n9. 無限感激所有為香港未來付出鮮血和生命的人民英雄，要求立法將6月9日定為香港法定紀念日<br />\n<br />\n10. 毋忘香港血色六月"},{"pid":"8937b06baca91fd2a538e47607e86abc1b95f52a","tid":1273293,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad5fa77c4ffcaef6d34e0dc2a8a1ee902381967e","tid":1273293,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18c6085ef112c57222d68394522c934c7b3b276","tid":1273293,"uid":40766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab5accf08f45329c2ac7de43af8d7192e027263","tid":1273293,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例風波，令香港人震怒。二百萬人上街反對，人數之多，全球各國未曾見，人類史上未曾見。<br />\n<br />\n六月以來，港人多日抗爭，用盡和平手段，流血流汗。惟始作俑者，特首林鄭月娥，紋風不動，鐵石心腸。冷血政權對民意視若無睹，三位年輕人先後以死相諫，令人痛心！<br />\n<br />\n我等香港人，為我城未來而焦急，為下一代性命安危而焦急！我等絕不容許再多一條生命犧牲。我等今集結於立法會中，重申五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1.完全撤回逃犯修例<br />\n2.追究警方開槍責任<br />\n3.不檢控及釋放示威者<br />\n4.撤銷定性6月12日集會為暴動<br />\n5.林鄭月娥問責下台<br />\n<br />\n我等現要求林鄭月娥本人親自到場回應。否則我等將持續佔領立法會，甚至廢除現有立法會，另組新議會，以全面反映民意。<br />\n<br />\n不撤、不散！"},{"pid":"0654d8b771aba85e374daf9bf267931dc7a91e7e","tid":1273293,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"搵十到二十個做代表讀宣言<br />\n中英對照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9aafd6bce5c8f48195e6104095fcce567fe40f","tid":1273293,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"English <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b78cca148a87e3ae8ae1ee99acd27d802c77b1","tid":1273293,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"唔好亂衝，定落嚟傾下一步"}]}